name: buffer overflow
description:
This is a unique plotter drawing, performed by intentionally provoking buffer overflows on a HP 7475A plotter. 

Edition 1/1. 
Original inmac felt-tip plotter pen on 200g/m² Hahnemühle paper 
29.7 x 42.0 cm
24.09.2021

The NFT comes with the original drawing, international shipping included. Upon resale on the secondary market the original drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping will be covered by the new owner.
